  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5617673/" class="title-link">《国学知识大全》，开示国学门径！！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5617673"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/60252357/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u60252357-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/60252357/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蕼年</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-10-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-10-15 09:49:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5617673_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         作为中国人，不能忘记传统；作为读书人，不以有不知国学。我们的国家，历史悠久，文化灿烂，源远流长，不输于任何一个民族。今天，随着国势的上升，我们更应该大力弘扬国学，向世界推介国学。成为文化大国才是真正的强国。吕思勉，中国著名的国学大师、史学家，他是中国...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 6没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
