        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36502893/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36502893/" class="">第2页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lostinkiss/" class=" " title="幽云十六州">幽云十六州</a>
                (男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36502893">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">今世之社会，皆为文明社会，其程度相差无几，善亦同善，恶亦同恶，故无何高下也。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-11-05 23:39</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>今世之社会，皆为文明社会，其程度相差无几，善亦同善，恶亦同恶，故无何高下也。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
